Terrorsaur:




Terrorsaur descended to the ground, spreading his wings, he caught an air 
current, leading him into the Predacon cave. He landed, flexing his wings on 
his spectacular maneuvers. He looked around the interior. Not any were 
inside. The only one that he saw was the mouse. He gurgled a growl to her. 
He didn't like her exactly. He didn't like the sight of Scorponok and her 
together.

He took two hops towards her.
